@fmuellner The above is the temporary conclusion of the lengthy discussion/investigation we have had on emacs-devel.

The latest branch can be read here: https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/emacs-devel/2020-02/msg00001.html, and it includes example patches for both options near the end.

It would be great to see even a quick response from Mutter developers, maybe acknowledging the side which has the bug in this situation. If someone has an idea for a simple workaround we could add to the upcoming release of Emacs, that would be even better.
